description: San Diego foodies have absolutely fallen for Brazilian Fusion Food Truck, thanks to their fantastically fresh flavors and wonderfully kind, friendly service. When you come by and try any of their empanadas, or plump and juicy meat & seafood skewers, or perhaps a hearty heap of Brazilian carne asada fries, you too will agree that you’ve found your new favorite food stop on the street.  For all this and much more, you must come out to the Brazilian Fusion Food Truck, you’re sure to have a beautifully delicious time.
name: Brazilian Fusion Food Truck
